## Button hierarchy

<!-- PARAMETERIZE: button_tier_list -->

Rules:

- Buttons always use sentence case with a focus ring.
- Icon sizes inside buttons are controlled by CSS descendant rules. Never set icon `font-size` inline inside a button.

